participants' knowledge regarding oral health of LTC residents and participants' 
oral health citation behavior. As the elderly population experiences an 
increased life expectancy with increased need for assistance with Activities of 
Daily Living (ADL), similar training programs will become an important factor in 
assessing the quality of care provided to LTC residents.

